{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-364-comfortable-distance","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 364: odgovarajuća udaljenost","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Postoji $N$ sedišta u jednom redu. $N$ ljudi dolazi jedan za drugim popunjavajući sedišta prema sledećim pravilima:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Ako postoji bilo koja stolica čije susedne stolice nisu zauzete, uzmi tu stolicu.</li>\n<li>Ako nema takve stolice, ali postoji bilo koja stolica čija je zauzeta samo jedna susedna stolica, uzmi tu stolicu.</li>\n<li>Inače, uzmi bilo koju od preostalih dostupnih stolica.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Neka je $T(N)$ broj mogućnosti na koje se $N$ sedišta popunjava sa $N$ osoba koristeći ova pravila. Sledeća figura pokazuje $T(4) = 8$.</p>\n<img alt=\"njia nane za viti N kujazwa na watu N\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/comfortable-distance.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Možemo potvrditi da $T(10) = 61\\,632$ i $T(1\\,000)\\bmod 100\\,000\\,007 = 47\\,255\\,094$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $T(1\\,000\\,000)\\bmod 100\\,000\\,007$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4d91000cf542c50ffea","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302025,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-364-comfortable-distance"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function comfortableDistance() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ncomfortableDistance();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.